14
[div class=p 
	"The MSX2 Vampire Killer was released in Japan, Europe and Brazil one month after the NES/Famicom Castlevania. 
	$LF
	"While the general outline and many elements are similar, the gameplay has a more nonlinear thing to it. 
	$LF
	"In every stage, you have to collect a white key to open the door to the next stage. 
	$LF
	"In addition, there is a plethora of other items to be found in chests, candles and walls. 
	$LF
	"This movie completes the game as fast as possible.
	$LF
]div
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
